      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The B-statistic is the posterior log-odds of differential expression... As well as gene ID and symbol, columns give chromosome location (Chr), log2-fold-change (logFC), average log2 expression (AveExpr), moderated t, P value, false discovery rate and B-statistic for each gene.",
      "asbval:note": "Table 1 output from limma topTable function includes both log-fold-change and B-statistic (posterior log-odds).",
