    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/differential-expression-result-interpretation/006",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "One popular differential expression pipeline is that provided by the limma software package... The limma pipeline includes linear modeling to analyze complex experiments with multiple treatment factors, quantitative weights to account for variations in precision between different observations, and empirical Bayes statistical methods to borrow strength between genes... The log-cpm values and associated weights are then input into limma's standard differential expression pipeline... The log-cpm values ygi and associated weights wgj are then input into limma's standard linear modeling and empirical Bayes differential expression analysis pipeline... The table shows output from the limma topTable function.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper explicitly names limma and describes lmFit (linear modeling), eBayes (empirical Bayes), and topTable (results extraction) functions.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1186-gb-2014-15-2-r29",
