      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/linear-model-fitting-for-gene-expression/008",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The log-cpm values ygi and associated weights wgj are then input into limma's standard linear modeling and empirical Bayes differential expression analysis pipeline.",
      "asbval:note": "Linear model outputs are explicitly used for downstream differential expression analysis via limma's empirical Bayes pipeline.",
