    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/method-comparison-differential-calls/005",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The results presented in this article were obtained using R version 3.0.0 and the software packages limma 3.16.2, edgeR 3.2.3, baySeq 1.14.1, DESeq 1.12.0, DSS 1.4.0, PoissonSeq 1.1.2 and tweeDEseqCountData 1.0.8.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms R as the programming environment and lists limma, edgeR, and other packages. However, ggplot2 is not mentioned; visualizations appear to use base R graphics and limma's built-in plotting functions (e.g., plotMA). Card claims ggplot2 but paper does not reference it.",
